data.description: Exceptional quality one story home on a breathtaking, low-maintenance 5-acre parcel located by the Tahoe National Forest for hiking, biking and fun!   Over 3500 of generous living, this beautiful home has a stunning living room with surrounding windows and sliding glass doors leading out to the fantastic deck looking into the forest!   Chef's kitchen with butlers' pantry and loads of cabinets with pull outs.   Formal dining room and a sweet parlor for home office or library.  5 car garage and 1100 s.f. shop and 2nd smaller shop is ideal for the hobbyist.    Custom coffered ceilings, 2X6 construction and loads of parking with the circular paved driveway!    Covered second porch is great for BBQ'ing year-round and nice sunshine and clearing around the property!   Circular paved driveway, top quality neighborhood with high end homes and beautifully maintained.    The serenity of this home and the land will fill your senses the moment you arrive!
